{"tid":1236263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林正財:林鄭積極考慮當面向市民致歉","createTime":"2019-06-17T11:33:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T13:00:03.000Z","uid":37757,"like":6,"dislike":461,"uniUserReply":118,"replies":[{"pid":"02055fdcbf5935eb85e6f3ce41e88ca78d55f55d","tid":1236263,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:33:42.000Z","msg":"政府日前宣布暫緩修訂《逃犯條例》，反激發近200萬人上街遊行要求撤回，行政長官林鄭月娥發聲明承認由於政府工作上的不足，令很多市民感到失望和痛心，為此向市民致歉。<br />\n<br />\n行政會議成員林正財說，林鄭月娥並非採取擠牙膏式道歉，據他所知，在第一次遊行前，政府已聽到聲音被指太傲慢，當時已期望與市民修復關係。<br />\n<br />\n他又稱，林鄭月娥昨晚聲明寫得十分有誠意，惟他承認由她面對面出來道歉更為理想，相信特首林鄭月娥正積極考慮中。<br />\n<br />\n林正財希望大家給林鄭月娥和團隊一個反思機會，對社會未來亦有正面意義。"},{"pid":"658968a934dc5c73b5fd02ee288c389e74348f49","tid":1236263,"uid":66099,"like":186,"dislike":0,"score":186,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:34:31.000Z","msg":"諗完就算？😂"},{"pid":"ed582fd8de5c22335c70a6cdea7e091656d4e393","tid":1236263,"uid":294,"like":68,"dislike":0,"score":68,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:34:34.000Z","msg":"無真誠就DQ 啦7婆"},{"pid":"a6946685f8354e881fc3ee62162f2dbbd2ca9c83","tid":1236263,"uid":6297,"like":107,"dislike":0,"score":107,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:35:02.000Z","msg":"咁都要考慮？"},{"pid":"0bd2629e20e23c0314f30c1dde4b57b50cb37135","tid":1236263,"uid":41389,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:35:04.000Z","msg":"道你老母<br />\n歉你老母"},{"pid":"921664b336e9bb1690ca40e0c055733842140e49","tid":1236263,"uid":116289,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:35:05.000Z","msg":"食撚屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"044f28af0d07f1dea499247e332a95bbe4303324","tid":1236263,"uid":108337,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:35:15.000Z","msg":"道歉都要考慮點道，on99"},{"pid":"94826a8ec50d9c2f12463c448a1058971518c56b","tid":1236263,"uid":133611,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:35:20.000Z","msg":"無人想聽你講野"},{"pid":"182e23dcdf7fe80e4ec9e